latestPosts.caption:
Hello beauties!! I hope you are having a good weekend♡
.
I have an awesome update!!
.
Yesterday was a huge day for me! I FINALLY got to see my neurosurgeon! 
My Mri was good🙌🙏The tumor did not grow back, and all the micro pieces are gone. I will continue to take my chemo and seizure pills for a while. I do my mri's every 2-3 months for the remainder of the year, to make sure the Astrocytoma doesn't come back. Then it will be every 6 months going forward.💗
All the pain, surgery, radiation, chemo, and personal issues... has made me a stronger person! 
I'm so thankful I got a picture with my neurosurgeon. He saved my life.🥲
Life is finally beginning for me again! A new start🙏 I'm so blessed and excited for my future 🤍
.
Thank you to everyone who has checked on my🤗
